description: An individual who reports belonging to the cultural gender role distinction of female.
An individual who reports belonging to the cultural gender role distinction of male.
An individual who does not identify as having any gender.
An individual who is not sure of their gender identity.
An individual who does not conform to a male/female gender identity.
An individual who describes their gender identity as fluctuating between male, female, and/or other.
An individual who does not subscribe to conventional gender distinctions but identifies with neither, both, or a combination of male and female genders.
A response indicating that an individual identifies with a gender category not included in the existing list of values.
A person whose gender identity or gender expression differs from their assigned sex.
